column5: We are going to Brett's silver birch camp this year on Corn Lake. I know it is a new camp. Any info on walleye fishing(locations, bait) in this lake would be appreciated and accomodations. Thanks.
Fish,Have fished Corn and other lakes at Silver Birch for 20 some years, e-mail me at [email protected] for infoLarry SNevada Walleye Man
